{"tid":765963,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"見住上証咁 一句講晒,只有光復東莞先救到國","createTime":"2018-08-03T08:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T11:30:15.000Z","uid":185416,"like":38,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"1c976e3370a3cd958ad83b6297a5ff069288c923","tid":765963,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:04:06.000Z","msg":"1.所謂十萬佳麗下嶺南，百萬嫖客上東莞，黃色行業一向可以帶動內需。估計每年做一億個嫖客、每個八百蚊。條數唔計比你聽都覺得可怕。仲要唔計被帶動嘅酒店、飲食、交通、娛樂等等等等收入。 請問有此福地，何惧美帝關税<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.增加就業人口，呢點唔洗講都知酒店、飲食、交通、娛樂都被帶動，一定要請人<br />\n<br />\n3. 可以促進人仔國際化，人仔淨流入&gt;淨流出。ISO聞名海外<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，開返東莞一定引一大班港人同洋腸去。如果每年有一億嫖客有一半係外國人。兌幾多人仔唔洗諗都知<br />\n<br />\n4.推動中港融合，一句問你 ISO/叫雞 定民主，我估九成半男人會簡叫雞，另外半成係gay佬。「內憂」港獨份子不打自降，「外患」美帝關税如浮雲。仲唔快啲光復!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講講下都幻想到光復美景，不如每個省都開一個「東莞」啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/160328_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F160328_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=712ba2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/160334_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F160334_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ebd6f404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/160339_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F160339_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3805b6af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fa0a9010c0b346f28fcd797f911473843a40691","tid":765963,"uid":41368,"like":13,"dislike":9,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"收皮啦雞蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e03fbc06c54c995de3031ea5f40dc2796d26a4d","tid":765963,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb803394c2d8c4dd26203ba15ef394ebf7e6703c","tid":765963,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7629b17f422f81a4